BT /F2 14 Tf 54 247 Td (1. Project Idea) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 219 Td (AgriSense backend is an agriculture recommendation system.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 196 Td (Its main job is to help a user answer questions like:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 173 Td (- Which crop is suitable for my location?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 158 Td (- What crops fit the current weather and soil?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 143 Td (- What is the historical weather trend in my area?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54 128 Td (- What should I know about irrigation, rainfall, and soil?) Tj ET
